e book |language=en |last=Mason |first=Fran |author-link1= |year=2003 |chapter=Mind Control |trans-chapter= |chapterurl= |chapter-format= |editor-last=Knight |editor-first=Peter |title=Conspiracy Theories in American History |url=http://cha3u.pbworks.com/w/file/fetch/45668088/Conspiracy%20Theories%20in%20American%20History%20%282003%29.pdf |location=Santa Barbara, California |publisher=ABC-CLIO, Inc. |pages=第483頁、第486-487頁 |isbn=9781576078129 |accessdate=2015-11-04 |ref={{harvid|Conspiracy Theories in American History|1979}} |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160427082827/http://cha3u.pbworks.com/w/file/fetch/45668088/Conspiracy%20Theories%20in%20American%20History%20%282003%29.pdf |archivedate=2016-04-27 }}</ref>。宗教和政治學者批評了凱茜的說法，因為缺乏任何支持性證據，並指出「從來沒有人因這種罪行被起訴，也沒有任何確鑿的證據」<ref name="Robertson2016">{{cite book |language = en|author=David G. Robertson|title=UFOs, Conspiracy Theories and the New Age: Millennial Conspiracism|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=4ngwCwAAQBAJ&pg=PT101|date=2016-02-25|publisher=Bloomsbury Publishing|isbn=978-1-4742-5322-2|pages=第101頁}}</ref>。

